FROM ghcr.io/xlionjuan/almalinux-bootc:base-docker@sha256:90bf667964c0a08a92a59fe8ddefc882ecdf0422b98d5b4281375b50c254d6a4

COPY build.sh /tmp/build.sh

RUN mkdir -p /var/lib/alternatives && \
    /tmp/build.sh && \
    dnf clean all && \
    rm -rf /var/log/* && \
    ostree container commit

RUN bootc container lint
